From: Alexander Hoffman <alxhoff@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Mar 2026 14:48:18 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 01/43] Add .gitignore for kernel tree and tools build
 artifacts

Ignore common build outputs including compiled objects, kernel images,
module files, and perf tool build artifacts to keep the working tree
clean.
---
 kernel/kernel/.gitignore | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/kernel/kernel/.gitignore b/kernel/kernel/.gitignore
index 44573c4b7..929054df5 100644
--- a/kernel/kernel/.gitignore
+++ b/kernel/kernel/.gitignore
@@ -176,11 +176,10 @@ x509.genkey
 *.kdev4
 
 # Clang's compilation database file
-compile_commands.json
+/compile_commands.json
 
 # Documentation toolchain
 sphinx_*/
 
 # Rust analyzer configuration
 /rust-project.json
-
-- 
